body:
### A little bit of this, a little bit of that
Starting new projects, time and time again, not getting very far along in completing them or turning them into success. It leaves me frustrated knowing that I have potential to achieve but have yet to find the way to get there. So once again, I am trying something out. Let's see where this takes me.
